== Relationship example
	
		Create a
		Java project called
		"de.vogella.jpa.eclipselink", create
		again a
		folder
		"lib" and place the
		required
		JPA jars and derby.jar into
		this folder.
	
	
		Create the
		`de.vogella.jpa.eclipselink.model`
		package
		and the following classes.
	
	
[source,java]
----
include::res/datamodel/Family.java[]
----
	
	
[source,java]
